Name: Frontline: ART Book vol.I USA
About the game: Unlock the secrets of World War II with this incredible limited-edition ART Book! This informative tome contains more than 130 pages-250+ images and descriptions of the most notorious American units of the war. With this book, you can become an expert on the history of World War II, from the brave soldiers on the frontlines to the daring strategies employed by commanders. Plus, when you purchase this book, you'll be contributing to the development of the 'Frontline game engine', helping to create even more thrilling and realistic strategy experiences for all fans of the genre. Don't miss out on this chance to make a difference and gain insight into the events of World War II – get your copy of the ART Book today! The 'Frontline Games Series' is a single developer effort, and I am deeply appreciative of all the feedback I receive. Every purchase you make helps me to create an even better strategy game for your enjoyment. *Friends, I am in need of your generous support to help raise the funds to upgrade the 'Frontline game engine'. Every purchase you make will go directly towards improving the games in the catalog. With your purchase, you will have the opportunity to add your name to the credits list. Simply send your desired name by email (mentioned in the official page) and you will be included in the credits list. Don’t miss out on the chance to be a part of the Frontline Games Series! Your contribution is greatly appreciated, thank you for your support!
